*Load Balancer* ( divide incoming traffic to multiple servers)
*Redis* (fast-memory: cashing:dynamically data(like user info) which use frequently store in it use RAM->fast memory meanwhile other data store in DB hard disk which is slow process)
working flow: data->check cash (data found return) ELSE->fetch from DB ->also save in cashe
*CDN(content delivery network)* for static data like images and videos , 
distributed network of edge server, static data upload to servers globally so user can access the data to its near server 
like if i have my main server in lahore and uer is in Newyork ,fetching dtaa from lahore would take time make high litency (delay) 
-solution:distrubute the data on edge globalyy servers

